org.apache.arrow.vector

Class UInt8Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.arrow.vector.BaseValueVector
      • org.apache.arrow.vector.BaseFixedWidthVector
        • org.apache.arrow.vector.UInt8Vector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<ValueVector>, FieldVector, FixedWidthVector, ValueVector, VectorDefinitionSetter

    public class UInt8Vector
extends BaseFixedWidthVector
    UInt8Vector implements a fixed width vector (8 bytes) of integer values which could be null. A validity buffer (bit vector) is maintained to track which elements in the vector are null.
